  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Shape the vision for education in emergencies</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Education is critical for all children, but it is especially urgent for the tens of millions of children affected by emergencies, be they man-made or natural disasters. To ensure that children have access to school during crises, there must be coordination to hear the voices of those who provide these services and support their work. This project will bring together policymakers and practitioners to ensure that all children and youth have safe, quality, relevant education in emergencies.</narrative>
  </description>
